## 🔄 Rollback Procedures

If deployment fails at any phase, follow these rollback procedures:

### Phase 01 Rollback (VPS Provisioning)
```bash
# Delete VPS instance
curl -X DELETE "https://api.{{vpsProvider.provider}}.com/v2/instances/$VPS_ID" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${{upper (snakeCase vpsProvider.provider)}}_API_KEY"

# Delete firewall group
curl -X DELETE "https://api.{{vpsProvider.provider}}.com/v2/firewall/$FIREWALL_ID" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${{upper (snakeCase vpsProvider.provider)}}_API_KEY"

# Delete SSH key
curl -X DELETE "https://api.{{vpsProvider.provider}}.com/v2/ssh-keys/$SSH_KEY_ID" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${{upper (snakeCase vpsProvider.provider)}}_API_KEY"
```

### Phase 02 Rollback (Appwrite Installation)
```bash
# Stop and remove all Appwrite containers
ssh -i {{security.sshKeyPath}} root@$VPS_IP "
  cd /opt/appwrite/appwrite
  docker-compose down -v
  rm -rf /opt/appwrite
"
```

### Phase 03 Rollback (DNS & SSL)
```bash
# Delete DNS A record
RECORD_ID=$(curl -s -X GET \
  "https://api.{{dnsProvider.provider}}.com/client/v4/zones/{{dnsProvider.zoneId}}/dns_records?name={{domain.appwriteSubdomain}}.{{domain.rootDomain}}" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${{upper (snakeCase dnsProvider.provider)}}_API_TOKEN" | jq -r '.result[0].id')

curl -X DELETE \
  "https://api.{{dnsProvider.provider}}.com/client/v4/zones/{{dnsProvider.zoneId}}/dns_records/$RECORD_ID" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${{upper (snakeCase dnsProvider.provider)}}_API_TOKEN"

# Remove SSL certificate
ssh -i {{security.sshKeyPath}} root@$VPS_IP "
  certbot delete --cert-name {{domain.appwriteSubdomain}}.{{domain.rootDomain}}
"
```

{{#if previewEnvironments.enabled}}
### Phase 04 Rollback (Preview Environments)
```bash
# Delete workflow file
rm .github/workflows/{{kebabCase projectName}}-preview.yml

# Delete all preview projects
for PR_NUM in $(gh pr list --json number -q '.[].number'); do
  curl -X DELETE "https://{{domain.appwriteSubdomain}}.{{domain.rootDomain}}/v1/projects/pr-$PR_NUM" \
    -H "X-Appwrite-Project: $APPWRITE_PROJECT_ID" \
    -H "X-Appwrite-Key: $APPWRITE_API_KEY"
done
```
{{/if}}

### Phase 05 Rollback (CI/CD)
```bash
# Delete workflow file
rm .github/workflows/{{kebabCase projectName}}-deploy.yml

# Revert to previous deployment
git revert HEAD
git push origin main
```

{{#if monitoring.enabled}}
### Phase 06 Rollback (Monitoring)
```bash
# Stop and remove monitoring stack
ssh -i {{security.sshKeyPath}} root@$VPS_IP "
  docker stop prometheus grafana alertmanager node-exporter cadvisor
  docker rm prometheus grafana alertmanager node-exporter cadvisor
  rm -rf /opt/monitoring /var/lib/prometheus
"
```
{{/if}}

